03 Hands-On Project
===================

- fleet management system

- designed for developers, DevOps
- use-case driven
- not going to into all the commands
- using pre-defined images loaded onto DockerHub
  - java-based
  - angular front-end
  - microservice architecture
    - a handful of microservices
  - tracking lorries

- start off w/basic prototype system
  - add layers

